==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A short, [[snort]]ing [[sound]], often to show disapproval, or used as a reply when one is reluctant to speak.
# The cry of a pig when it makes its [[snort]]ing [[cry]].
# A family of ''[[Perciformes]]'' [[fish]] of the family ''[[Haemulidae]]''

====Derived terms====
*[[grunt boy]]
*[[grunt work]]

